::Prowl::

Prowl looks into Iron Raptor's optics as she kisses him, his optics full of 
love. He watches her as she steps away, Prowl a bit reluctant to let her out 
of his sight again. He watches the chamber door close, taking a few steps 
back to sit down on a chair.

He waits for the CR chamber to finish its job, thinking of how he'd make Iron 
Raptor at home when they got some time to themselves.
